[media] v4l2: replace s_mbus_fmt by set_fmt in bridge drivers

Replace all calls to s_mbus_fmt in bridge drivers by calls to the
set_fmt pad op.

Remove the old try/s_mbus_fmt video ops since they are now no longer used.

